<h2 id="head-4c4a2e80cc873135b3d277a22b6e85110c509731">Disclaimer</h2>

    <ul>

 This has no theme and nothing in special. It will have some races and classes I'd like to play on ToME along with certain combinations. Keep in mind that I have practicaly no time to work on it so updates will be rare. <p>
 I will take suggestions for race/classes, but nothing complex since I have no idea how to work my way around with Lua. 
</p>

    </ul>


<h2 id="head-9c74fb571984d7f3e781ea8b013e5f74bcd16389">Change Log</h2>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Changes for the next version 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Maiar wont agravate anymore 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Minor Spell tweaking 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Small bug fixing 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Maylith's cat gets more hp now <img src="./wiki/classic/img/smile.png" alt=":)" height="15" width="15"> 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Changed skill points to 7 per level. I thought only 6 wasn't being enough to compensate the fact that you lost all natural internal skill leveling. So yeah, now you get more to put on combat, sneakiness, magic and spirituality. 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 New spells: 
</p>
</li>

